</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【報價】Sony APS-C 新旅遊、拍片廣角鏡      SEL15F14G、SEL11F18、SELP1020G 試相 + 香港售價</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/02/sony-apsc/dc/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-apsc</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jun 2022 12:41:08 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[數碼相機]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102933</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>好多朋友影相都想裝備要夠輕，易於攜帶，影相拍片一整天手部都不會感到疲倦。Sony 今日就發佈了 3 支 APS [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>好多朋友影相都想裝備要夠輕，易於攜帶，影相拍片一整天手部都不會感到疲倦。Sony 今日就發佈了 3 支 APS-C 片幅 E-Mount 相機專用的超廣角定焦、變焦鏡頭，特別適合行山、拍攝旅遊風光，又或者自拍影片專用。當中最大光圈的一支為 SEL15F14G，15mm 焦距之下帶來 F/1.4 大光圈，鏡身只有 219g，極為輕巧易用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-694x380.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-694x380.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-1280x700.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-768x420.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-1536x840.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-2048x1120.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC08541-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC00010" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116749571/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116749571_5db2dae09e_b.jpg" alt="DSC00010" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>今次 Sony 一口氣發表 3 支 APS-C 片幅的 E-Mount 鏡頭，特別適合 a6600、a6500、ZV-E10 等 APS-C 片幅的 Sony E-Mount 相機，當然也適用於全片幅相機如 a73、a74，甚至旗艦機 a1 等等（其實有些全片幅相機用家都會買 APS-C 鏡頭，勝在夠輕便！）。這 3 支鏡頭都是廣角、超廣角鏡頭，包括有：</p><h2>高解像廣角 G 鏡頭 SEL15F14G<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>高解像廣角 G 鏡頭，F1.4 大光圈，15mm 焦距（相等於 35mm 片幅的（下稱等效焦距）22.5mm），在拍攝人像相片時可將更多背景收入在相片中，大光圈讓人像相片散景的淺景深效果更加淺，同時適合行山旅遊之用。機內裝設有雙線性馬達，讓 AF 對焦更快更靈敏，對焦系統也壓制了呼吸效應。其 0.17m 最近對焦距離，可讓你輕鬆拍攝近物，而背後帶來一大片強烈散景，最適合拍攝小物、體積細小的擺設。</p><p>建議零售價 $5,990</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-768x522.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011.jpg 882w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="502" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC00001" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116999389/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116999389_c7eb063a1f_b.jpg" alt="DSC00001" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00008" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52117258975/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52117258975_96050f4756_b.jpg" alt="DSC00008" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00011" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116999309/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116999309_0a5b7c1d84_b.jpg" alt="DSC00011" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00015" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116749021/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116749021_4b5bb6d23b_b.jpg" alt="DSC00015" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00048" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116788418/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116788418_31cb7f9656_b.jpg" alt="DSC00048" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00056" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116748851/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116748851_792e0cecdc_b.jpg" alt="DSC00056" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00062" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52117258665/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52117258665_e9350ffd7e_b.jpg" alt="DSC00062" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00052" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116748736/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116748736_6c328de9fe_b.jpg" alt="DSC00052" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00054" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116788218/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116788218_7c0f64df6f_b.jpg" alt="DSC00054" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>入門級定焦超廣角鏡頭 SEL11F18<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>入門級定焦超廣角鏡頭，11mm 焦距（等效焦距 16.5mm）F/1.8 大光圈，可為背景帶來強烈散景效果，拍攝風景、風景＋人像合用，也適合拍攝自拍 Vlog 的朋友。內置雙線性馬達提升 AF 對焦靈敏度，也改善呼吸效應。最短對焦距離可達 0.12m，同樣適合拍攝小物、小擺設，極近攝影距離帶來更好的散景效果。</p><p>建議零售價 $4,290</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-694x430.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="430" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-694x430.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-768x476.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012.jpg 812w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019.jpg" alt="" width="611" height="444" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC00018" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52115768227/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52115768227_307e086f50_b.jpg" alt="DSC00018" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>超廣角變焦鏡頭新版本 SELP1020G</h2><p>這支新 G 鏡是過往 E 10-18mm F4 OSS 的最新版本。G 鏡頭除改善相片周邊成像，鏡身做得更加細小，重量只有 178g，為目前全球最輕的超廣角 APS-C 變焦鏡頭。它擁有 F/4 恆定光圈，同時採用內對焦、內變焦設計，即使變焦、對焦鏡頭內部都不會伸出來，除令拍攝更靈活方便，使用相機穩定器的專業用戶，也毋須擔心變焦後需要重新調節穩定器的重心。新鏡也內置了全新電動變焦系統，ZV-E10、FX3 用戶更可透過快門鍵旁邊的變焦撥桿，進行過渡柔順的變焦，對於拍攝 Vlog 的用戶就更加方便。新鏡焦距更開闊到 10mm 至到 20mm，最長等效焦距可達到 30mm，用來拍攝街頭景色就更加靈活，完美覆蓋超廣角至到廣角段。</p><p>建議零售價 $5,990</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0033.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0033-694x403.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="403" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0033-694x403.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0033-768x446.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0033.jpg 915w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0029.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0029.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="484" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC00021" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52117047104/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52117047104_252bc2e85c_b.jpg" alt="DSC00021" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00023" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52116999249/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52116999249_97e3d986cd_b.jpg" alt="DSC00023" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00027" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52117265870/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52117265870_91e81b2839_b.jpg" alt="DSC00027" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>SELP1020G @10mm</p><p><a title="DSC00032" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/52115729752/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52115729752_4c50e99739_b.jpg" alt="DSC00032" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>SELP1020G @20mm</p><p>以上 3 支鏡頭現時已可在 Sony Store 預訂。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
