</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Mercedes-AMG One 超跑量產版，道路版 F1 最高馬力達 1063 匹</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/02/mercedes-amg-one/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=mercedes-amg-one</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jun 2022 10:00:48 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mercedes-AMG One]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102853</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>平治汽車發表了他們最新量產版超級跑車 Mercedes-AMG One。此車在 2017 年最先以概念車身份登 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>平治汽車發表了他們最新量產版超級跑車 Mercedes-AMG One。此車在 2017 年最先以概念車身份登場並稱為「Mercedes-AMG Project One」終在今年推出 275 部限量生產版本。而在概念車發表當時這一批限量被已經被預訂一空，每部 Mercedes-AMG One 售價為 270 萬美元（約港幣 2118 萬元）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713147.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102874" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713147-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713147-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713147-768x456.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713147.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713162.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713162-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713162-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713162-768x488.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713162.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713130.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713130-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713130-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713130-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713130.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/29-normal690-7713154.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713131.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713131-694x440.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713131-694x440.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713131-768x487.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713131.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713132.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713133.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713133-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713133-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713133-768x518.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713133.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>工程師一直渴望把 F1 一級方程式賽車的引擎裝在一部超跑裡面，如今這部車終有機會在街頭見到。這部 Mercedes-AMG One 擁有 F1 技術的 1.6 升 V6 油電引擎再加 4 副電動摩打，引擎轉速可達 11000 轉，引擎加摩打的綜合最高馬力可達 1063 匹，起步至到時速 100 公里只需要 2.9 秒，起步至時速 200 公里亦只需要 7 秒，汽車最高時速可達 352 公里。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713129.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713129-694x477.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="477" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713129-694x477.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713129-768x528.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713129.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713128.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713128-694x429.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713128-694x429.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713128-768x475.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713128.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Mercedes-AMG One 外型極似一部勒芒 24 小時耐力賽的原型賽車，而車門採用上掀式設計，軚盤亦有非常接近 F1 賽車的設計，旁邊同樣有數碼大熒幕儀錶板。而這部車由於採用特殊動力系統，需要每 5 萬公里就要回廠進行保養。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713146.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713146-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713146-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713146-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713146.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713159.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713159-694x435.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713159-694x435.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713159-768x481.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713159.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713148.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713148-694x484.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="484" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713148-694x484.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713148-768x535.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7713148.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.roadandtrack.com/news/a40164244/2023-mercedes-amg-one/">Road and track</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
