ty Room 玩都一樣方便。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">指定型號名單：</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Intehill:</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">HS156PEQ (Intehill 15.6&#8243; QLED 便攜式顯示器 HS156PEQ)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">H156PQT (Intehill 15.6&#8243; QLED 輕觸控便攜式顯示器 H156PQT)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">HS156KNP (Intehill 15.6&#8243; 4K 便攜式顯示器 HS156KNP)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">HS173PC (Intehill 17.3&#8243; FHD 144Hz 便攜式顯示器 HS173PC)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">GMKtec:</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Xpanel (GMK Xpanel 14&#8243; 4K UHD 便攜式觸控顯示器)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Xpanel 2 (GMK Xpanel2 15.6&#8243; 4K UHD 便攜式觸控顯示器)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1102523 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-636x900.jpg" alt="" width="636" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-636x900.jpg 636w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-410x580.jpg 410w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/001-scaled.jpg 1131w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 636px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">*遊戲禮品需於網上兌換，禮品為實體禮品。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">**優惠數量有量，送完即止。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">活動兌換網址：<a href="https://forms.gle/DXZ92t2igiwX12ZCA">https://forms.gle/DXZ92t2igiwX12ZCA</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">更多便攜螢幕資料：<a href="https://bit.ly/3wKTQcp">https://bit.ly/3wKTQcp</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
