</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>蘋果新專利 Apple Watch 相機鏡頭，外媒：恐有隱私問題</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/02/apple-watch-camera-2/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-watch-camera-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[NatalieFu]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jun 2022 08:53:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[潮流手錶]]></category><category><![CDATA[apple watch]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102833</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日前美國專利商標局公佈， Apple 申請 Apple Watch 加入鏡頭的專利獲批。據悉，Apple 打算 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日前美國專利商標局公佈， Apple 申請 Apple Watch 加入鏡頭的專利獲批。據悉，Apple 打算將相機鏡頭加入 Apple Watch 內，用戶就可以透過設定慣用手勢，於錶冠拍攝相片。</p><p>Apple 獲批的專利名為「擁有鏡頭的手錶」，據專利圖表顯示，Apple Watch 中的鏡頭有內置發光器，既可以自動調節照度、亦適用於相機閃光燈。</p><p>專利報告建議，Apple Watch 鏡頭加入可置於旋轉的錶冠中，並設於錶盤的光圈後，令光學感應器可協助相機捕捉場景，亦能為錶盤感應器作感知旋轉輸入。但 Apple Watch 的鏡頭只能用作拍照及拍攝短片用，用戶未必能使用該鏡頭進行 Facetime 通訊，或其他功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1102835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6a0120a5580826970c02942fad6948200c-800wi-370x580.jpeg" alt="" width="370" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6a0120a5580826970c02942fad6948200c-800wi-370x580.jpeg 370w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6a0120a5580826970c02942fad6948200c-800wi-574x900.jpeg 574w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6a0120a5580826970c02942fad6948200c-800wi-768x1205.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6a0120a5580826970c02942fad6948200c-800wi.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 370px" /></p><p>有很多人擔心 Apple Watch 內置相機鏡頭帶來的私隱問題，Apple 在公佈專利時足足強調了七次有關 Apple Watch 新增鏡頭的專利設計對私隱問題私的重視。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.patentlyapple.com/2022/05/apple-has-won-a-patent-for-a-future-apple-watch-with-an-integrated-camera-in-its-digital-crown-and-more.html">Patently Apple</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
